{"id": 2925, "genre": 1001, "title": "生活中你觉得什么时候才算是“属于自己的时间”？", "description": "手机没信号的几分钟，反而觉得好像拥有了真正的“me time”。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA Images）", "record_count": 3673, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190429171945MYzwHKdtuZ6XbImN.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-04-30T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 341760, "content": "洗澡", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360615}, {"id": 341761, "content": "不用带小孩的所有时刻", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1646836}, {"id": 341762, "content": "晚上熬夜", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1489977}, {"id": 342274, "content": "辞掉工作的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1629537}, {"id": 341763, "content": "打球 吃饭 洗澡哈哈😄", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1634769}, {"id": 342019, "content": "在交通工具上的时候 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1296611}, {"id": 342275, "content": "临睡觉之前", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 830923}, {"id": 341764, "content": "一杯美式  一根香烟  一首钢琴曲 的静谧街角", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1632633}, {"id": 342020, "content": "可口可乐了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1196734}, {"id": 341765, "content": "只有游泳跑步的时候了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527822}, {"id": 342021, "content": "期末考试的时候，自己的时间真实到不能再真实", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1646728}, {"id": 341766, "content": "熬夜的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1437910}, {"id": 342022, "content": "听歌的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1628065}, {"id": 341767, "content": "戴上耳机的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 391490}, {"id": 341768, "content": "划掉待办事项清单的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 73, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 954437}, {"id": 341769, "content": "上下班在出租车上且司机不主动搭话的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1527911}, {"id": 342025, "content": "做梦的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1621804}, {"id": 343561, "content": " 。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1605759}, {"id": 341770, "content": "晚上喝两杯啤酒抽一支烟的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1494337}, {"id": 342026, "content": "做梦时", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1647197}, {"id": 341771, "content": "睡前刷牙的三分钟", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 882780}, {"id": 342027, "content": "静默的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1622264}, {"id": 341772, "content": "健身的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 78, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1117113}, {"id": 342028, "content": "放假不用早起窝在被窝里玩手机的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1647203}, {"id": 341773, "content": "自己打游戏不被人打扰", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1408819}, {"id": 342029, "content": "在旅行的路上", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1647204}, {"id": 341774, "content": "一个人待在房间的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1539682}, {"id": 342030, "content": "不用再去思考或计划接下来要做什么，不因下一步计划而逼着自己做某个决定或选择时，这才是我自己的时间.", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1647206}, {"id": 341775, "content": "上课路上戴上耳机的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1339725}, {"id": 342031, "content": "写剧本的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1405298}, {"id": 341776, "content": "宿舍里的人都回家了，只剩我一个人的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 260, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359635}, {"id": 342032, "content": "坐在客厅里，静静得听楼上小姐姐的动静", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1412346}, {"id": 342033, "content": "洗澡的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537109}, {"id": 341778, "content": "戴上耳机摘下眼镜放下手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1570397}, {"id": 342034, "content": "睡觉的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955457}, {"id": 341779, "content": "手机没电，电脑没网", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540310}, {"id": 342035, "content": "睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1606593}, {"id": 341780, "content": "停车场里一个人坐在车里的时候 洗澡的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 868692}, {"id": 342036, "content": "什么都不做，什么都不想，什么都不用去管你只需要自己花好自己的时间的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1563399}, {"id": 342037, "content": "做自己想做的事并乐在其中！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1647074}, {"id": 341782, "content": "读书、写字，听歌，都是自己的呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1499657}, {"id": 342038, "content": "晚上熄灯熬夜时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1647230}, {"id": 342039, "content": "读书的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616753}, {"id": 341784, "content": "睡前一个人在房间写日记的半小时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1628980}, {"id": 342040, "content": "下班回家，坐在楼下的车里熄掉发动机四周全黑的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1560914}, {"id": 341785, "content": "冲咖啡的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640226}, {"id": 342041, "content": "上卫生间的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 823182}, {"id": 342553, "content": "异地工作，周末突然闲下来没人找，书和电影看不进去，睡觉睡不踏实心里发慌，有种和世界的抽离感。这时候，\"自己\"的感觉格外强烈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1648575}, {"id": 341786, "content": "打开纸质书看，听着轻音乐时", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955454}, {"id": 342042, "content": "分手之后", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475977}]}